t-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-[#f0ede8]","children":"One sentence:"}]," A boutique marketing agency serving 22 clients replaced a 3-person reporting function with a Claude-based workflow — saving 143 hours/month and $8,200/month in labor — without losing a single client in the transition."]}]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-4","children":"The Case Study"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4 text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Meridian Creative (name changed) is a 15-person performance marketing agency in Austin, TX. Monthly retainer revenue: $340K. Client count: 22. Their problem was one that every agency owner recognizes immediately: the monthly report was killing them."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Each client got a custom PDF report: Google Ads performance, Meta results, SEO movement, content metrics. A senior account manager spent roughly 2 hours per client pulling data from four platforms, drafting narrative commentary, and formatting the document. With 22 clients and a 4-person account team rotating the work, reporting consumed 44 hours every month — nearly a full week of a senior hire's time — before the actual client calls even happened."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"They had tried a BI tool (Looker Studio). The templates were rigid, the commentary was absent, and clients kept asking for the \"story\" anyway. They had tried delegating to a VA. Data accuracy issues resulted in a client threatening to cancel. They were stuck."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The solution they built: a Python script that pulls raw data from Google Ads API, Meta Ads API, Google Analytics 4, and Ahrefs — all into a structured JSON payload — then passes it to Claude via the API with a carefully engineered system prompt containing: the agency's house voice, each client's specific goals and benchmarks, any month-specific context the account manager adds in 3 minutes, and output formatting instructions for a Notion template."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Claude generates the full narrative commentary: trend analysis, anomaly explanations, strategic recommendations for next month, and the executive summary. The account manager reviews, tweaks maybe 2 sentences, exports to PDF. Total time per client: 45 minutes down from 2 hours. Total monthly savings: 27 hours. Annualized: 324 hours recovered."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-[#111111] border border-[#1e1e1e] p-6","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-5","children":"The Numbers"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6","children":[["$","div","Hours saved/month",{"className":"space-y-1","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#5a5550] uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Hours saved/month"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[18px] font-mono text-[#f0ede8] number-stat","children":"16.5 hrs"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[12px] font-mono text-[#c9a84c]","children":"−27.5 hrs"}]]}],["$","div","Labor cost saved",{"className":"space-y-1","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#5a5550] uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Labor cost saved"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[18px] font-mono text-[#f0ede8] number-stat","children":"$$600/mo"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[12px] font-mono text-[#c9a84c]","children":"−$8,200/mo"}]]}],["$","div","Implementation cost",{"className":"space-y-1","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#5a5550] uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Implementation cost"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[18px] font-mono text-[#f0ede8] number-stat","children":"$$4,200 one-time"}],""]}],["$","div","Claude API cost/mo",{"className":"space-y-1","children":[["$","d